st class facilities to support our academics and students as they work on many of the worldâ€™s most important issues.</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="ls-row-clr"></div></div></div><div class="ls-row" id="ls-row-3"><div class="ls-fxr"><div class="ls-area" id="sitename"><div class="ls-area-body"><div class="ls-cmp-wrap ls-1st" id="w1363649825000"><div class="iw_component" id="1363649825000"><div id="heading"><h2>Centre for Biological Sciences</h2></div></div></div></div></div><div class="ls-row-clr"></div></div></div><div class="ls-row" id="container"><div class="ls-fxr"><div class="ls-area" id="ls-row-4-area-1"><div class="ls-area-body"><div class="ls-cmp-wrap ls-1st" id="w1363649825001"><div class="iw_component" id="1363649825001"><div id="navposdefault"><div id="nav"><ul><li id="searchBox"><form action="https://search.sharepoint.soton.ac.uk/Pages/results.aspx"  method="get"><fieldset><input class="text" id="searchText" name="k" value="Search" type="text"/><button class="submit" type="submit" name="submit">Submit</button><span id="rad"><label for="here" title="search only the Biological Sciences site">This site</label><input id="here" checked="checked" name="s" title="search only the Biological Sciences site" type="radio" value="Biological Sciences"/><label for="there" title="search all University of Southampton sites">University</label><input id="there" value="All" name="s" title="search all University of Southampton sites" type="radio"/></span></fieldset></form></li><li class="home"><a href="/biosci/index.page?">Home</a></li><li class="pages"><ul><li class="inactive"><a href="/biosci/about/index.page?" target="" title="">Who we are</a></li><li class="inactive"><a href="/biosci/research/index.page?" target="" title="">Research</a></li><li class="inactive"><a href="/biosci/undergraduate/index.page?" target="" title="">Undergraduate study</a></li><li class="inactive"><a href="/biosci/postgraduate/index.page?" target="" title="">Postgraduate study</a></li><li class="inactive"><a href="/biosci/international/index.page?" target="" title="">International</a></li><li class="inactive"><a href="/biosci/business_partnership/index.page?" target="" title="">Enterprise</a></li><li class="inactive"><a href="/biosci/alumni/index.page?" target="" title="">Alumni</a></li><li class="inactive"><a href="/biosci/outreach/index.page?" target="" title="">Outreach</a></li><li class="inactive"><a href="/biosci/news/index.page?" target="" title="">News, events &amp; seminars</a></li><li class="inactive"><a href="/biosci/contact.page?" target="" title="">Contact us</a></li></ul></li><li class="sotonhome"><a href="http://www.southampton.ac.uk/" title="University of Southampton home page">University Home</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="ls-area" id="content"><div class="ls-area-body"><div class="ls-cmp-wrap ls-1st" id="w1363649825002"><div class="iw_component" id="1363649825002"><div class="intro"><p>Our world-leading research in the areas of molecular and cellular bioscience, biomedical sciences (particularly neuroscience and development), ecology and the environment focuses on addressing today's key challenges. Furthermore, our range of biological sciences degrees comprise programmes in biochemistry, biology, biomedical sciences, pharmacology and zoology - covering the whole spectrum and helping our students secure a rewarding future career.</p></div></div></div><div class="ls-cmp-wrap" id="w1363649825003"><div class="iw_component" id="1363649825003"><div class="itemContainer"><div class="highlightBox left"><h2>Applying science to life, tackling global issues</h2><img src="/assets/imported/transforms/site/home/Item_Thumb/101E41E7DE01490DB0590ED8525A40C0/DSC_0253.JPG_SIA - JPG - Fit to Box_80_160.jpg" alt="Research" class="right"/><p>From climate change to human health, our groundbreaking research in Biological Sciences tackles key global issues and offers solutions to many of life's challenges.</p><p><a href="/biosci/research/index.page">Find out more</a></p></div><div class="highlightBox right"><h2>Providing the foundation for a successful career</h2><img src="/assets/imported/transforms/site/home/Item_Thumb/1B5215485EB34906A8BC27A3B1561770/DSC_0702.tif_SIA - JPG - Fit to Box_80_160.jpg" alt="Biological Sciences building" class="right"/><p>Biological Sciences' broad-based BSc programmes give our undergraduates the opportunity to study a wide range of topics and discover their talents before specialising.</p><p><a href="/biosci/undergraduate/index.page">Find out more</a></p></div><div class="highlightBox left"><h2>Creating the bioscientists of the future</h2><img src="/assets/imported/transforms/site/home/Item_Thumb/EA81E26EB9CC43A89B1B1A4983B26DE3/collecting scat.JPG_SIA - JPG - Fit to Box_80_160.jpg" alt="Postgraduate study" class="right"/><p>Postgraduates benefit from our world-leading facilities, excellent academic support from our Graduate School, and collaborative approach through the new Institute for Life Sciences.</p><p><a href="/biosci/postgraduate/index.page">Find out more</a></p></div><div class="highlightBox right"><h2>Working with industry and community partnerships</h2><img src="/assets/imported/transforms/site/home/Item_Thumb/42F9E8111B8F419B9DC605C4A1AAB8C7/134404.JPG_SIA - JPG - Fit to Box_80_160.jpg" alt="business partnerships" class="right"/><p>Our expert knowledge of the life sciences places us in a key position to contribute our scientific expertise to projects and develop innovative solutions for a wide range of partners.</p><p><a href="/biosci/business_partnership/index.page">Find out more</a></p></div><div class="clear"><!--clear--></div></div><div class="news"><h2>Latest News</h2><ul class="news"><li><p class="date">2013/11/26</p><p>New technique for testing drugs to treat cystic fibrosis and epilepsy</p><p><a href="/biosci/news/2013/11/26_new_technique_for_testing_drugs_to_treat_cystic_fibrosis_and_epilepsy.page">
